nks==\n*[http://www.bmwopen.de Official website]\n\n{{BMW Open tournaments}}\n{{2013 ATP World Tour}}\n\n[[Category:Bavarian International Tennis Championships|2013 BMW Open]]\n[[Category:2013 ATP World Tour|BMW Open]]\n[[Category:2013 BMW Open]]\n[[Category:April 2013 sports events in Europe]]\n[[Category:May 2013 sports events in Europe]]\n", "text_old": "{{TennisEventInfo|2013|BMW Open|\n| date=29 April &nbsp;\u2013 5 May\n| edition=98th\n| category=[[ATP World Tour 250 series]] \n| draw=28S / 16D\n| surface = [[Clay court|Clay]]\n| prize_money=\u20ac467,800\n| location=[[Munich]], Germany\n| venue=MTTC Iphitos\n| champs={{flagicon|GER}} [[Tommy Haas]] <ref name=ms>{{cite web|title=2013 Munich Men's Singles draw|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/en/scores/archive/munich/308/2013/draws?matchtype=singles|publisher=[[Association of Tennis Professionals]] (ATP)}}</ref>\n| champd={{flagicon|FIN}} [[Jarkko Nieminen]] / {{flagicon|RUS}} [[Dmitry Tursunov]] <ref name=md>{{cite web|title=2013 Munich Men's Doubles draw|url=http://www.atpworldtour.com/en/scores/archive/munich/308/2013/draws?matchType=doubles|publisher=[[Association of Tennis Professionals]] (ATP)}}</ref>\n}}\n\nThe '''2013 [[BMW Open]]''' was a men's [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Clay court|outdoor clay courts]]. It was the 98th edition of the event, and part of the [[ATP World Tour 250 series]] of the [[2013 ATP World Tour]]. It took place at the [[MTTC Iphitos]] complex in [[Munich]], Germany, from 29 April through 5 May 2013. Third-seeded [[Tommy Haas]] won the singles title.\n\n==Singles main draw entrants==\n\n===Seeds===\n{| class=wikitable\n|-\n! width=\"70\"| Country\n! width=\"175\"| Player\n! Rank<sup>1</sup>\n! Seed\n|-\n|{{flag|SRB}}\n|[[Janko Tipsarevi\u0107]]\n|10\n|1\n|-\n|{{flag|CRO}}\n|[[Marin \u010cili\u0107]]\n|11\n|2\n|-\n|{{flag|GER}}\n|[[Tommy Haas]]\n|14\n|3\n|-\n|{{flag|GER}}\n|[[Philipp Kohlschreiber]]\n|21\n|4\n|-\n|{{flag|UKR}}\n|[[Alexandr Dolgopolov]]\n|23\n|5\n|-\n|{{flag|GER}}\n|[[Florian Mayer]]\n|29\n|6\n|-\n|{{flag|RUS}}\n|[[Mikhail Youzhny]]\n|30\n|7\n|-\n|{{flag|AUT}}\n|[[J\u00fcrgen Melzer]]\n|34\n|8\n|}\n* Rankings are as of April 22, 2013.\n\n===Other entrants===\nThe following players received [[Wild card (sports)|wildcard]]s into the main draw:\n* {{flagicon|GER}} [[Tobias Kamke]]\n* {{flagicon|GER}} [[Kevin Krawietz]]\n* {{flagicon|FRA}} [[Ga\u00ebl Monfils]]\n\nThe following players received entry from the qualifying draw:\n* {{flagicon|GER}} [[Matthias Bachinger]]\n* {{flagicon|KAZ}} [[Evgeny Korolev]]\n* {{flagicon|POL}} [[\u0141ukasz Kubot]]\n* {{flagicon|AUS}} [[John Millman]]\n\nThe following player received entry as lucky loser:\n* {{flagicon|UKR}} [[Sergiy Stakhovsky]]\n\n===Withdrawals===\n;Before the tournament\n* {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Thomaz Bellucci]]\n* {{flagicon|BEL}} [[Xavier Malisse]]\n* {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Bernard Tomic]]\n\n==Doubles main draw entrants==\n\n===Seeds===\n{|class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n|-\n! width=\"70\"| Country\n! width=\"175\"| Player\n! width=\"70\"| Country\n! width=\"175\"| Player\n! Rank<sup>1</sup>\n! Seed\n|-\n|{{flag|AUT}}\n|[[Alexander Peya]]\n|{{flag|BRA}}\n|[[Bruno Soares]]\n|38\n|1\n|-\n|{{flag|AUT}}\n|[[J\u00fcrgen Melzer]]\n|{{flag|IND}}\n|[[Leander Paes]]\n|43\n|2\n|-\n|{{flag|AUT}}\n|[[Julian Knowle]]\n|{{flag|SVK}}\n|[[Filip Pol\u00e1\u0161ek]]\n|57\n|3\n|-\n|{{flag|CZE}}\n|[[Franti\u0161ek \u010cerm\u00e1k]]\n|{{flag|SVK}}\n|[[Michal Merti\u0148\u00e1k]]\n|86\n|4\n|}\n* Rankings are as of April 22, 2013.\n\n===Other entrants===\nThe following pairs received wildcards into the doubles main draw:\n* {{flagicon|GER}} [[Matthias Bachinger]] / {{flagicon|GER}} [[Daniel Brands]]\n* {{flagicon|GER}} [[Tommy Haas]] / {{flagicon|CZE}} [[Radek \u0160tep\u00e1nek]]\n\n==Champions==\n\n===Singles===\n{{main|2013 BMW Open&nbsp;\u2013 Singles}}\n* {{flagicon|GER}} [[Tommy Haas]] defeated {{flagicon|GER}} [[Philipp Kohlschreiber]], 6\u20133, 7\u20136<sup>(7\u20133)</sup>\n\n===Doubles===\n